<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at main -->

## What's Changed
### SemVer Patch
* Add support for streaming on recent Darwin platforms by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/24
* Use APIs available on older macOS in tests by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/25
* Add missing transition AsyncBackpressuredStream state machine by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/27
* Improve debug logging and add tests that it is not evaluated when disabled by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/26
* Avoid double continuation resume in URLSession delegate in corner case by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/28
* Replace AsyncBackpressuredStream with updated implementation by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/29
### Other Changes
* Add docker-compose file for 5.10 CI by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/16
* Enable documentation comment validation in swift-format by @PARAIPAN9 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/18
* Bump swift-format to 5.9 by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/17
* Add a soundness --fix flag by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/19
* Disable warnings as errors in nightlies by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/21
* Disable "respectsExistingLineBreaks" in .swift-format for more consistent styling by @PARAIPAN9 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/20
* Add README badges by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/23

## New Contributors
* @PARAIPAN9 made their first contribution in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/18

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/compare/0.3.0...0.3.1
title: Swift OpenAPI URLSession 0.3.1

## What's Changed
### SemVer Major
* Move to Swift 5.9 as the minimum version by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/32
### SemVer Minor
* Improve inlining by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/30
* Remove AsyncStream.makeStream backports now we support only Swift 5.9+ by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/34
### SemVer Patch
* Add missing available annotation to streaming tests by @simonjbeaumont in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/33
### Other Changes
* Prep for 1.0 alpha, adapted to runtime changes in main by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/31
* Bump to 1.0.0-alpha.1 by @czechboy0 in https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/pull/36


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apple/swift-openapi-urlsession/compare/0.3.1...1.0.0-alpha.1
